Install Hadoop
$ ./hadoop-create.sh

Use New Shell
$ exec bash

Initialise Hadoop
$ ./hadoop-initialise.sh 

Unset existing SSH enviroment
$ unset SSH_AUTH_SOCK
$ unset SSH_ASKPASS

Generate New SSH Keys
$ ./hadoop-ssh-keys.sh 

Verify Hadoop is not running
$ ./hadoop-status.sh		# check if hadoop is running

Start Hadoop
$ ./hadoop-start.sh		# start hadoop

Verify Hadoop is running
$ ./hadoop-status.sh		# check if hadoop is running

Run Hadoop Jobs Repeatedly
$ ./hadoop-pizza.sh		# submit pi calculation jobs 
				# in a loop

Observe
1. HDFS GUI
access t1.daddylabs.com:50070 in firefox

2. Map Reduce GUI
access t1.daddylabs.com:50030 in firefox
